      "content": "i get that it's risky a bit but i've heard some people say that if you keep the levels steady in your blood by taking small doses frequently it works better than waiting for the pain to spike. if i just take a smaller dose like 200mg every 2 hours instead, would that be a safer way to keep the inflammation down so i can actually work?",
